parameters.name: Domain
parameters.description:
The domain name of the website.

>  A forwarding rule must be configured for the domain name. You can call the [DescribeDomains](~~91724~~) operation to query all domain names.

parameters.name: Owner
parameters.description:
The source of the rule. Valid values:

*   **manual** (default): manually created.
*   **clover**: automatically created. Specify this value when you want to delete intelligent protection rules.

parameters.name: RuleNames
parameters.description: The names of the rules that you want to delete.
